{"tid":528242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民熱話：偷拍天后酒店住客性交　再有新片流出！ (20:51)","createTime":"2018-01-13T14:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T15:35:24.000Z","uid":61277,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"53dcba9b2934ea388b0997a1a6f376844544d63c","tid":528242,"uid":61277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T14:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180113/photo/bkn-20180113205108607-0113_00822_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180113%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180113205108607-0113_00822_001_01b.jpg&h=9a013395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=Vn3LUO3Df2simmiD%2FmGVfI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=69d0cd15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】天后一間酒店疑再有房內交歡片段曝光！最新流出的片段比上兩段質素不同，懷疑是不同人所為，亦未知與前兩段片屬同一日拍攝。是次片段中，一對男女在床上交歡過程全被拍下，拍攝者在高處拍下較低層的房間情況。警方則回覆指，調查仍在進行，暫時未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n從網上最新流出的片段所見，拍攝者從遠處，拍攝疑是同樣是天后一間酒店的房間內情況。該片長逾4分鐘，只見房內全身赤裸的兩名男女，半趴在床上有交歡的動作。至片段結尾，二人雙雙在床上相擁。期間片段拍攝一方傳有玻璃杯碟碰撞的聲音，但未有人作聲。<br />\n<br />\n該間位於天后的酒店標榜設置落地大玻璃窗，讓住客欣賞維港景色。不少遊客都慕名而來，在酒店房間內拍下以維港寫真。不過，懷疑有不法之徒趁機在酒店遠處的大廈設置攝錄機，拍下住客的一舉一動並上傳至互聯網，有觸犯《個人資料（私隱）條例》之嫌。警方發言人今日回應指，對偷拍事件，調查仍在進行當中，暫時未有人被捕。"},{"pid":"64073a63be52004822b3eb394123032508588285","tid":528242,"uid":61653,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T14:35:01.000Z","msg":"人地爆房扑野都要偷拍<br />\n真係痴撚線"},{"pid":"e5c2b56c5c48f257453c0e5f66f7357c1e7e620b","tid":528242,"uid":45368,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T14:36:12.000Z","msg":"仆你個街，片呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c94c7e27de2d2b2874756527bc86442f8dd9fe","tid":528242,"uid":77453,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T14:37:31.000Z","msg":"片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6ad568e973654d25a225180597321462bc9079","tid":528242,"uid":162653,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T14:38:42.000Z","msg":"本身見個景咁靚都想住晚睇下景影下相<br />\n而加不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce3acf1440e0ab4eeb22f2aaa9ab9438fa766f8","tid":528242,"uid":142233,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T14:46:36.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"83755a096288573df8d5833bc88c9dbb5ab2c665","tid":528242,"uid":134227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T14:51:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lm</blockquote><br />\nlm"},{"pid":"14c4e7545a77e23e37a07f3d060897034d1a1ced","tid":528242,"uid":32380,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T14:54:39.000Z","msg":"我有3條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c866ff95cd4c500a340c3a30b808d13ab7a8d9b","tid":528242,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T15:14:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11ed471bc533daa8d1ad8c9b70545ecb1170704f","tid":528242,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T15:28:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母瘋傳總無連登份</span>"},{"pid":"18837f5dcfe835958356df12a3e911276d142993","tid":528242,"uid":3023,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T15:28:34.000Z","msg":"每次瘋傳都係冇連登份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f400bed74d4a618bea54a390a78df7c10a9898a","tid":528242,"uid":9104,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T15:32:17.000Z","msg":"網絡孤島"},{"pid":"f5d6b9f3f91516bb593d792962507e141c0eb913","tid":528242,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T15:35:24.000Z","msg":"avgle 咪有囉 你班友唔係冇上網睇av 習慣呀？"}]}